{"tid":2359221,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"衰妹沈月天寒地凍着背心晒腿 賀《入樽》出動畫版電影","createTime":"2021-01-08T17:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T13:20:50.000Z","uid":44730,"like":28,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"140b9854f4da11b3874d76e38d725bb0bfe14875","tid":2359221,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"經典日本籃球漫畫《男兒當入樽》（Slam Dunk）在1990年開始連載，去年踏入30周年，至今仍是不少人心目中的神級漫畫，去年推出手機遊戲亦大受歡迎。日前《入樽》作者井上雄彥在個人twitter上公佈，將會推出《入樽》動畫版電影，令不少《入樽》迷未睇先興奮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qavz9Kc-8li_FZTUZ-vXBsEkOqE=/468x702/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZQITSG2ZCJGQ7F2LD6HVQKXA54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fqavz9Kc-8li_FZTUZ-vXBsEkOqE%3D%2F468x702%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZQITSG2ZCJGQ7F2LD6HVQKXA54.png&h=ab0d5672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n穿上芝加哥公牛隊籃球背心的沈月，大晒白滑長腿。"},{"pid":"16df78a09b43f96a5824d4cd9598d50c77d68c05","tid":2359221,"uid":44730,"like":18,"dislike":87,"score":-69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pEAzrQ4qa8fgRYXtS-lZHJtyhgk=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V2QRE2FDC5BU3D6XYCC5DKUIRY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpEAzrQ4qa8fgRYXtS-lZHJtyhgk%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV2QRE2FDC5BU3D6XYCC5DKUIRY.png&h=5098259e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民質疑她純粹幫老竇時裝店賣廣告。"},{"pid":"48eccfc318280058a5fee235a69cf646c89824e1","tid":2359221,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"現時已有動畫版電影的官方網站，但就尚未加入詳細內容，而《入樽》出動畫電影消息一出，即吸引到邱淑貞大女、有「最美星二代」之稱的沈月注意。今日她在IG貼出一輯穿上芝加哥公牛隊籃球背心的照片，下身則大晒一雙白滑長腿，在天寒地凍下擺出多個不同甫士。她以日文寫道：「真係會拍戲？不如大家一齊睇。」有網民讚她像極漫畫中女主角晴子，不過亦有網民質疑以她的年紀，《入樽》漫畫對她應該頗陌生，指她之所以穿成這樣，純粹是幫老竇時裝店宣傳而已。"},{"pid":"8ea878841dbbbb1871e16b5b8cd0785b14fd6e2c","tid":2359221,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":61,"score":-59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hcyXjjuMDhkf4NkaJKv8XpI3OBw=/802x1427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ADN4GCTVW5BRVFDW6RB6TKVE3Y.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhcyXjjuMDhkf4NkaJKv8XpI3OBw%3D%2F802x1427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FADN4GCTVW5BRVFDW6RB6TKVE3Y.JPG&h=f83dd99b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BLwM--MKhwzcQvTepirCx3ukQYQ=/802x1425/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RNFAJMKPABAO7IUUHPTHUIP2DY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBLwM--MKhwzcQvTepirCx3ukQYQ%3D%2F802x1425%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRNFAJMKPABAO7IUUHPTHUIP2DY.png&h=4693f995&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be6ffa4f7a96e011af612351547b7fba73da73dc","tid":2359221,"uid":49859,"like":124,"dislike":10,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"啲人話唔正，我屌埋佢地嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05c0a66e60743d0fe84d45017ae47a9375f8003","tid":2359221,"uid":44730,"like":24,"dislike":20,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T17:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZdpGRspdYvi-aclQ7AoGikb25j4=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IH7KUESBQJDP5MKPFVVDD7MJ3A.j